{"tid":685163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放生還放死？ 他一個手滑 上千條錦鯉全被噴到草地上...","createTime":"2018-05-31T07:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T19:04:54.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a47a13c28316c7132a89c48ba72e76aaf81f1841","tid":685163,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/155459_6f81b52ca4e8d01ef2ee7d3809437f16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F155459_6f81b52ca4e8d01ef2ee7d3809437f16.png&h=f6e193f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕這樣是在放生還是在「放死」？中國山東省臨沂大學受到漁業公司捐贈3000條日本錦鯉和1萬條鰱魚，預計要放養在校內文學院的湖中，不料工人一個手滑，大量的錦鯉和水就這樣噴到湖邊的草地上，令現場圍觀群眾全部傻掉。<br />\n而圍觀群眾看著在草地上掙扎彈跳的錦鯉，趕緊蹲下來把錦鯉一一丟入湖中，臨沂大學事後則將「事故照片」放在微博上，並強調：「這些魚不能隨意打撈。」<br />\n許多中國網友看到錦鯉就這樣跟著水噴到草地上，紛紛無奈地說：「為什麼要放在草坪上？」、「哪有這樣放生的，有沒有常識？」、「錦鯉到底得罪了誰？」、「無腦的都是放死啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/155517_4940cda0336f196da99bbdb152afae88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F155517_4940cda0336f196da99bbdb152afae88.png&h=5a9d7106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2442946\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2442946&d=gGPc9fZ3kzy84puXdouW0hOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=831e21d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2442946&h=88a6681d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2442946</a>"},{"pid":"d77c7a5636fbd45b8b9a806233d128b1ba43f6c8","tid":685163,"uid":14918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T07:58:17.000Z","msg":"咪住先, <br />\n中國土地養日本魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a61b69471dc046d6372fad1d2e8e527dc5a68c","tid":685163,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T08:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 執返幾條返屋企 今晚加餸"},{"pid":"ff2d80df32ed4fc0049ba05e898bd9f560a58c52","tid":685163,"uid":45627,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T08:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hahatai.com/sites/default/files/u1031/5_160.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hahatai.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fu1031%2F5_160.jpg&h=c3cde66e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efda78a5fd367e3b3c7b63bc3809f74cb6e70ae9","tid":685163,"uid":103325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T19:04:54.000Z","msg":"就算響個湖到，轉頭咪又係俾班生蕃捉咗去食"}]}